<!-- ====== 模块2: 九州食图 ====== -->
<section class="food-section" id="module2">
  <div class="food-section-inner">
    <div class="food-module-title food-reveal">
      <span class="module-num">贰 · 地域风味</span>
      <h2>九州食图</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">一方水土一方食，八大地域的中秋味觉记忆</p>
    </div>
    <div class="region-grid">
      <div class="region-card region-featured food-reveal">
        <span class="rc-icon">🥮</span>
        <div>
          <span class="rc-region">华南 · 广东</span>
          <div class="rc-name">广式月饼</div>
          <p class="rc-desc">皮薄馅足、松软细腻，莲蓉蛋黄为经典代表。广式月饼占据全国市场份额半数以上，是最具影响力的月饼流派。糖浆皮的发明使月饼得以长久保存，远销海外。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="steam-burst"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="region-card food-reveal">
        <span class="rc-icon">🍘</span>
        <span class="rc-region">华东 · 江苏</span>
        <div class="rc-name">苏式月饼</div>
        <p class="rc-desc">酥皮层次分明、入口即化。鲜肉月饼趁热食用最为美味，咸甜兼备，流行于江浙沪地区。</p>
        <div class="steam-burst"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="region-card food-reveal">
        <span class="rc-icon">🍪</span>
        <span class="rc-region">华北 · 北京</span>
        <div class="rc-name">京式月饼</div>
        <p class="rc-desc">甜度适中、口感酥松，自来红、自来白是经典代表。传承宫廷风味，古法制作，历史悠久。</p>
        <div class="steam-burst"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="region-card food-reveal">
        <span class="rc-icon">🥞</span>
        <span class="rc-region">西南 · 云南</span>
        <div class="rc-name">滇式月饼</div>
        <p class="rc-desc">火腿入馅、咸香独特。云腿月饼搭配玫瑰花瓣，咸甜交融的地方风味，极具西南特色。</p>
        <div class="steam-burst"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="region-card food-reveal">
        <span class="rc-icon">🥧</span>
        <span class="rc-region">华南 · 潮汕</span>
        <div class="rc-name">潮式月饼</div>
        <p class="rc-desc">朥饼酥香、芋泥细腻。猪油起酥、绿豆沙馅，潮汕工夫茶的最佳伴侣，传统手工制作。</p>
        <div class="steam-burst"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="region-card food-reveal">
